，做出不一样的判断。","totalCount":1248,"users":[{"userVid":68728833,"name":"_Kirito","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/DYAIOgq83eo694TUavtW1742UKfqL8k9hRGebibGWr6DtBJrxZD4uYKoULLGV9vNN3XSo6nFvcNt3TXGGZWNRBA/132","isV":0,"vDesc":"Vincent van Gogh"},{"userVid":14407682,"name":"翁小娴。 🌴","nick":"翁小娴。 🌴","gender":2,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/PiajxSqBRaEJ7LRdJBB4WvPbW3wnEBrGIldpg9jgNy2gNPX1k5UPiamg/0","isV":0,"vDesc":"迟缓的脚步跟不上躁动的心"},{"userVid":15636484,"name":"iam 小胖友贩卖员","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/XLmrEdZTk98bmNwwtjRsVfflQ91Ipuyrb1QkibFpGm59xrlVfeF41kkNovpSTAib4oemUuvF4VwbLJia0FewXgt1w/132"}]},{"bookId":"26640431","userVid":257056130,"bookmarkId":"26640431_27_3054-3210","chapterUid":27,"range":"3054-3210","markText":"所谓“有效策略适用的时空尺度”，是指如果我们认为一个策略有效时，一定要问自己，这是短时有效，还是长期有效？是局部有效还是整体有效？因为在微观环境下有效的策略，在宏观系统下就可能完全无效甚至有害；把短期有效的策略放到长期视角下也可能带来负面的结果。我们必须根据自己要解决问题的范围和周期，有针对性地选择不同的策略。","totalCount":1242,"users":[{"userVid":12029953,"name":"宸汐","gender":0,"avatar":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/n1T7AyD5S8k4Kv5OheZ3AVzxIgibXl8NNF1EVcWdfOOVMN865LLO2Sz1iaEribdkETkwcGOQFFbNzhliaZ6wic78Ulw/132"},{"userVid":14407682,"name":"翁小娴。 🌴","nick":"翁小娴。 🌴","gender":2,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/PiajxSqBRaEJ7LRdJBB4WvPbW3wnEBrGIldpg9jgNy2gNPX1k5UPiamg/0","isV":0,"vDesc":"迟缓的脚步跟不上躁动的心"},{"userVid":75921411,"name":"好运百分百","nick":"好运百分百","gender":2,"avatar":"https://res.weread.qq.com/wravatar/WV0003-Sklql~8x5mAX_fmmxDUfMaa/0"}]},{"bookId":"26640431","userVid":20699383,"bookmarkId":"26640431_23_3080-3160","chapterUid":23,"range":"3080-3153","markText":"所谓能够把跨学科知识“融会贯通”，本质上就是有能力看到不同的领域面对着哪些相似的问题，在处理这些相似的问题时，不同领域有哪些有效策略可以相互借鉴。","totalCount":1196,"users":[{"userVid":37970944,"name":"李思挂","gender":2,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/eHEMOF2hOekZicUiaQt34Rtvvg6RQJ7zaBku717PliaLv9JgR8MMyibhhA/0"},{"userVid":75921411,"name":"好运百分百","nick":"好运百分百","gender":2,"avatar":"https://res.weread.qq.com/wravatar/WV0003-Sklql~8x5mAX_fmmxDUfMaa/0"},{